and islands further east. combined bus and ferry services will take you to destinations in java such as yogyakarta. the gili islands are three tiny islands off lombok. a backpacker favourite fast going upmarket and easily accessed by direct boat services. komodo is an island and national park in east nusa tenggara. the island is famous for the komodo dragon. accessible most easily by air via labuan bajo on flores. flight time 80-90 min. lombok is an unspoiled island east of bali with beaches, waterfalls and volcanoes. direct boat services or 20 min by air. yogyakarta has convenient air service 